Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在中国科技巨头的版图中，很少有人物能像王兴这样具有关键性地位。\NIn the landscape of China's tech giants, few figures are as pivotal as Wang Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他是美团的创始人，这是一家全球最大的按需配送平台。\NHe is the founder of Meituan, the world's largest on-demand delivery platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但成功并非一蹴而就。\NBut success didn't come easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他的早期职业生涯充满了接连不断的失败。\NHis early career was marked by serial failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他眼看着自己的创业项目一个个倒下，面对不断下滑的数据潸然泪下，但他从未放弃。\NHe watched his startups collapse, weeping over declining numbers, yet he never gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,2010年，他创办了美团。\NIn 2010, he launched Meituan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它最初从团购业务起步，后来发展成一款重塑城市生活的超级应用。\NIt started with group buying but evolved into a super-app that reshaped urban life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,其逻辑简单却强大：\NThe logic was simple but powerful:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.08,0:00:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,通过一支庞大的骑手队伍，将饥饿的消费者与本地商家连接起来。\NConnect hungry customers with local businesses through a vast army of riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.12,0:00:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如今，数百万身穿黄色外套的骑手穿梭在中国的大街小巷，成为城市物流的“血管”。\NToday, millions of riders in yellow jackets navigate the streets of China, becoming the veins of the city's logistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,王兴的愿景并不止于餐饮。\NWang Xing’s vision went beyond just food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他希望打造“城市生活的操作系统”。\NHe wanted to build the "operating system for city life."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它成为了一条生命线。\NIt became a lifeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当你生病在家时，骑手可以在几分钟内送来药品。\NWhen sick at home, the riders deliver medicine within minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,出行时呢？\NTraveling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以即时预订酒店和机票。\NYou can book hotels and flights instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,美团几乎覆盖了日常生活的方方面面。\NMeituan covers almost every aspect of daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然而，这种高效率是有代价的。\NHowever, this efficiency comes at a cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,系统由一套冷酷的算法驱动，为每一单配送计算最短时间。\NThe system is driven by a ruthless algorithm that calculates the shortest time for every delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,骑手往往被困在系统之中。\NRiders are often trapped in the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为了避免超时罚款，他们被迫与时间赛跑，甚至无视交通规则。\NTo avoid fines for late deliveries, they are forced to race against the clock, ignoring traffic rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这种“速度至上”的需求导致交通事故激增。\NThis "need for speed" has led to a surge in traffic accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,消费者的便利，有时是建立在骑手安全风险之上的。\NThe convenience of the customer is sometimes built on the safety risks of the riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这引发了公众的愤怒和抗议。\NThis sparked public outrage and protests.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,骑手们要求更好的待遇、保险以及更合理的配送时间。\NRiders demanded better treatment, insurance, and more reasonable delivery times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,王兴和美团面临着巨大的压力。\NWang Xing and Meituan faced immense pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,公众开始质疑：技术是在服务人类，还是在奴役人类？\NThe public began to question: Is technology serving humanity, or enslaving it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,王兴的事业无疑推动了中国的现代化。\NWang Xing’s work has undeniably modernized China.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但他的故事也为全球敲响了警钟。\NBut his story serves as a global lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的创新不仅仅关乎效率，\NTrue innovation isn't just about efficiency;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,更在于在利润与社会责任之间取得平衡。\Nit's about balancing profit with social responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这既是王兴面临的挑战，也是整个科技未来的挑战。\NThis is the challenge for Wang Xing, and for the future of tech.
